    =< @end_of_embargo_without_year
    | .

p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 30px 0 30px 0;"
  strong
    | We do encourage you to privately make publicity arrangements for the announcement on
    =< @end_of_embargo_without_year
    | .

p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 30px 0 30px 0;"
  strong
    | Terms of the Embargo

p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 0 0 30px 0;"
  | We will provide Awards information to the media in mid-April, including a list of Recipients and their press contact details, so that they can prepare news articles for release on
  =< @media_deadline
