p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 0 0 30px 0;"
  | The list of Recipients will be published in the supplement to the London Gazette on the announcement day
  =< link_to "https://www.thegazette.co.uk/awards-and-accreditation/content/kings-awards-for-enterprise",
