    target: '_blank', rel: 'noreferrer nofollow', title: 'opens in a new window'

p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 0 0 30px 0;"
  | Prior to the official announcement on
  =< @end_of_embargo_without_year
  | , you may be contacted by the press regarding your Award. You are permitted to speak to them; however, this will be under embargo conditions. You are also permitted to approach your own press contacts to arrange media coverage of your Award.
  strong
    |  However, please make it clear to anyone that you approach in the media, that they cannot publish anything until after
    =< @end_of_embargo_with_time
    | .

p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 30px 0 30px 0;"
  strong
    | 2. Approve your Press Book entry, which must be a factual account of why you have achieved the Award.

div style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 30px 0 30px 0;"
